flowchart LR
    classDef exp fill:#0B1F5F,color:#FFFFFF,stroke:#0B1F5F,stroke-width:2px;
    classDef app fill:#1F4EAA,color:#FFFFFF,stroke:#1F4EAA,stroke-width:2px;
    classDef ai fill:#00A3E0,color:#FFFFFF,stroke:#0077A6,stroke-width:2px;
    classDef data fill:#EAF1FF,color:#0B1F5F,stroke:#1F4EAA,stroke-width:1.5px;

    U[Enterprise Users<br/>AI Engineers / Analysts]:::exp --> W[Next.js Webapp]:::app
    W --> BFF[Next.js API Proxy]:::app
    BFF --> API[FastAPI Orchestration Layer]:::app

    API --> ING[Ingestion Catalog JSON]:::data
    API --> MILVUS[(Milvus Vector DB)]:::data
    API --> OPENAI[OpenAI Embeddings + LLM]:::ai
    API --> PROMPTS[PromptOps Store<br/>prompts/*]:::ai

    DS[(Workspace Data<br/>dataset/*)]:::data --> PIPE[Ingestion Pipeline]:::app
    PIPE --> ING

    ING --> IDX[Artifact Indexer]:::app
    IDX --> MILVUS
    IDX --> OPENAI

    DOCS[(Platform Docs<br/>.docx)]:::data --> DOCING[Doc Ingestion Pipeline]:::app
    DOCING --> MILVUS
    DOCING --> OPENAI

    SUM[Summary Indexer]:::app --> MILVUS
    SUM --> OPENAI
    PROF[Profile Indexer]:::app --> MILVUS
    PROF --> OPENAI

    AIR[Airflow Scheduler]:::app --> PIPE
